1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,310 --> 00:01:42,270
[I Don't Want to be Friends With You]

3
00:01:46,930 --> 00:01:48,210
Step aside. I'll grab it.

4
00:01:48,300 --> 00:01:50,289
Fine. I don't believe you can.

5
00:01:50,380 --> 00:01:51,750
Left, left, left...

6
00:02:09,990 --> 00:02:11,110
See?

7
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:13,400
We're just so unlucky.

8
00:02:13,490 --> 00:02:15,220
We can depend on nobody.

9
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:18,820
Hey, you...

10
00:02:21,970 --> 00:02:22,470
Bad machine!

11
00:02:22,470 --> 00:02:25,320
[Episode 8]

12
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,390
Li Jin Bu.

13
00:02:26,490 --> 00:02:28,610
How about buying you a doll?

14
00:02:28,810 --> 00:02:34,140
[Defeated Mother-Daughter Soldiers]

15
00:02:38,490 --> 00:02:39,770
Look at that.

16
00:02:40,010 --> 00:02:40,700
That's why

17
00:02:40,790 --> 00:02:42,590
you can never get good grades.

18
00:02:42,970 --> 00:02:44,800
Good for your class discipline.

19
00:02:44,890 --> 00:02:46,880
How dare you sleep like that in my lesson!

20
00:02:46,970 --> 00:02:47,720
Wu Zhi Xun.

21
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:48,950
Wake her up.

22
00:02:49,050 --> 00:02:50,480
I must ask her

23
00:02:50,570 --> 00:02:51,720
how well she's learned

24
00:02:51,810 --> 00:02:54,030
so that she doesn't take my lesson.

25
00:02:57,410 --> 00:02:59,070
Wake her up.
What are you waiting for?

26
00:03:01,850 --> 00:03:02,680
Sir.

27
00:03:02,770 --> 00:03:04,160
She isn't sleeping on purpose.

28
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:05,630
She's sick today.

29
00:03:07,530 --> 00:03:09,020
Do you think I believe you?

30
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,480
How dare you pretend to be sick?

31
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:12,250
Do you believe I'll tell your parents?

32
00:03:12,370 --> 00:03:13,420
Sir.

33
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,470
She really is sick.

34
00:03:16,670 --> 00:03:17,660
Just now,

35
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:18,960
her forehead was covered in sweat

36
00:03:19,170 --> 00:03:20,579
and her face was also pale.

37
00:03:20,770 --> 00:03:21,880
I think,

38
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:23,190
it doesn't seem to be a fake.

39
00:03:23,350 --> 00:03:24,180
Sir,

40
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,560
I understand that you don't believe me,

41
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:28,470
but at least you should believe
what Wu Zhi Xun said.

42
00:03:40,850 --> 00:03:42,310
How do you feel now?

43
00:03:45,660 --> 00:03:46,970
Can you still take the lesson?

44
00:03:47,370 --> 00:03:48,990
Yeah, definitely...

45
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:50,320
Okay, then,

46
00:03:50,420 --> 00:03:51,930
you can just rest on the table.

47
00:03:52,020 --> 00:03:52,760
After class,

48
00:03:52,850 --> 00:03:54,390
you should go to the infirmary.

49
00:03:56,329 --> 00:03:58,240
All right, class! Look at the blackboard!

50
00:03:58,590 --> 00:03:59,860
For this exercise,

51
00:03:59,950 --> 00:04:02,460
I'll teach you the solution one last time.

52
00:04:02,570 --> 00:04:04,110
Listen carefully!

53
00:04:18,850 --> 00:04:21,570
Did you really stay up
to revise last night?

54
00:04:24,730 --> 00:04:26,320
It's true.

55
00:04:26,410 --> 00:04:28,550
I swear on my name.

56
00:04:29,130 --> 00:04:30,590
Don't do that anymore.

57
00:04:36,210 --> 00:04:37,340
I'm going out for a while.

58
00:04:45,690 --> 00:04:46,450
Li Qing Tong.

59
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:48,110
Good on you!

60
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:50,520
Even Wu Zhi Xun started to speak for you.

61
00:04:51,409 --> 00:04:52,780
What are you talking about?

62
00:04:52,870 --> 00:04:54,590
Leave me alone!

63
00:04:55,460 --> 00:04:56,340
Tong.

64
00:04:57,820 --> 00:04:58,659
Sleep on this.

65
00:04:58,730 --> 00:04:59,610
It's more comfortable.

66
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,500
Shui Shui is the best!

67
00:05:04,620 --> 00:05:05,830
Just sleep for a while.

68
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,200
Don't sleep in the next lesson.

69
00:05:07,290 --> 00:05:09,350
Got it.

70
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:13,230
No,

71
00:05:13,330 --> 00:05:15,100
there must be something strange behind it.

72
00:05:16,290 --> 00:05:18,200
Why didn't he speak for me?

73
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,330
-Get out.
-What...

74
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:20,620
Leave her alone.

75
00:05:21,330 --> 00:05:23,310
Why didn't he speak for me?

76
00:05:23,650 --> 00:05:24,790
There must be something wrong with him.

77
00:05:25,850 --> 00:05:27,190
He didn't speak for me...

78
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:38,210
Mr Liu

79
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:39,750
Yes?

80
00:05:41,470 --> 00:05:42,400
I'm sorry.

81
00:05:43,909 --> 00:05:45,090
What happened?

82
00:05:46,290 --> 00:05:47,780
I just lied to you.

83
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:49,810
Li Qing Tong is not sick.

84
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:51,830
I know.

85
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,740
I'm not an idiot, okay?

86
00:05:54,450 --> 00:05:55,120
But,

87
00:05:55,210 --> 00:05:57,320
in order to finish
the learning task I gave to her,

88
00:05:57,409 --> 00:05:58,980
she didn't sleep at all last night.

89
00:05:59,070 --> 00:06:00,710
That's why she fell asleep in your lesson.

90
00:06:01,330 --> 00:06:02,880
I'm the main cause of her mistake,

91
00:06:02,970 --> 00:06:04,590
so please don't blame her.

92
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,020
I can prove it to you

93
00:06:06,260 --> 00:06:07,920
that she did do it for her studies.

94
00:06:10,550 --> 00:06:12,690
Okay, I believe you.

95
00:06:12,770 --> 00:06:13,980
But you should remind her

96
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:15,800
that one should study in a scientific way,

97
00:06:15,890 --> 00:06:17,400
not stay up all night.

98
00:06:17,490 --> 00:06:19,630
One can never study well
if one's worn out.

99
00:06:20,530 --> 00:06:21,550
Thank you, sir.

100
00:06:21,730 --> 00:06:23,070
I'll talk to her.

101
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:24,620
Okay, you may go.

102
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:34,440
Li Qing Tong always ranked
outside of 100.

103
00:06:34,650 --> 00:06:36,470
Telling me she stayed up to study?

104
00:06:36,770 --> 00:06:38,680
Somehow, I find it hard to believe.

105
00:06:39,290 --> 00:06:40,680
Let me tell you, Mr Liu.

106
00:06:40,770 --> 00:06:43,360
Never look down upon their ambition.

107
00:06:43,450 --> 00:06:45,590
Do you know why I split them
into groups like that?

108
00:06:45,730 --> 00:06:47,540
Those brats from Class 3

109
00:06:47,770 --> 00:06:49,590
never listen to their parents.

110
00:06:49,810 --> 00:06:51,650
If you criticize them, they'd fight back.

111
00:06:51,730 --> 00:06:53,409
You can only take advantage
of their own ambition

112
00:06:53,490 --> 00:06:54,409
to point them in the right direction.

113
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:56,070
That's the proper way.

114
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:57,760
A million words from us

115
00:06:57,850 --> 00:06:59,790
cannot compete with one word
from their friend.

116
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:01,690
That makes sense.

117
00:07:02,150 --> 00:07:03,210
Those brats

118
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:04,880
are really tiring us out!

119
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:08,150
You didn't listen to a word
in the maths class,

120
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:09,720
so I have to teach you

121
00:07:09,810 --> 00:07:11,230
the whole maths lesson today.

122
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,140
You slept for half of the English class,

123
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:14,920
and 15 minutes in the politics class.

124
00:07:15,010 --> 00:07:16,360
I wrote down the points for you.

125
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:18,050
You should review them all over again.

126
00:07:18,130 --> 00:07:19,160
Are you clear?

127
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:24,480
Forget it.

128
00:07:24,570 --> 00:07:26,030
Go home and sleep.

129
00:07:29,650 --> 00:07:31,080
Why did you stop?

130
00:07:31,290 --> 00:07:33,220
You cannot learn anything
in such a condition.

131
00:07:33,310 --> 00:07:34,400
Go home and sleep.

132
00:07:34,490 --> 00:07:35,590
Let's do it tomorrow.

133
00:07:42,540 --> 00:07:43,830
Oh, the school is over.

134
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:46,220
Give me the exam paper you've done before.

135
00:07:46,330 --> 00:07:47,470
Only for Maths.

136
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:19,140
Li Qing Tong, turn the light off.

137
00:08:25,290 --> 00:08:26,320
You didn't recite much at night,

138
00:08:26,410 --> 00:08:27,790
but slept for a whole day.

139
00:08:28,170 --> 00:08:29,300
Not useful at all!

140
00:08:46,210 --> 00:08:48,150
Drink the milk while it's hot.

141
00:08:48,310 --> 00:08:49,730
Okay. Thanks, Mum.

142
00:08:58,330 --> 00:08:59,960
Mum, please leave.

143
00:09:00,050 --> 00:09:01,430
I need to study.

144
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:15,260
[Compendium of History
of European Philosophy]

145
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:16,470
Another student's exam paper?

146
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:18,040
Yes.

147
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:20,930
I can clearly distinguish
our son's handwriting.

148
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:22,880
I could tell it was not his.

149
00:09:24,610 --> 00:09:25,910
At first glance,

150
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:28,150
I could tell there were
many mistakes on the paper.

151
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,750
It must belong to a bad student.

152
00:09:33,290 --> 00:09:34,470
I'm wondering

153
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:36,590
what he's up to.

154
00:09:36,930 --> 00:09:37,810
Darn.

155
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:38,970
I must ask him.

156
00:09:39,490 --> 00:09:41,030
Don't be in a rush.

157
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,180
He's now

158
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:44,200
in a period of rebelling.

159
00:09:44,290 --> 00:09:46,020
Don't always clash with him.

160
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:47,640
In my opinion,

161
00:09:47,730 --> 00:09:48,930
looking at another one's papers

162
00:09:49,020 --> 00:09:51,150
is also related to study.

163
00:09:51,370 --> 00:09:52,300
Later,

164
00:09:52,470 --> 00:09:54,360
I'll try and find out
in a roundabout way.

165
00:09:54,450 --> 00:09:55,680
Leave him alone for now.

166
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,620
You must pay attention to him.

167
00:09:57,780 --> 00:09:59,200
He will soon take his third year.

168
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:01,240
We cannot slack off even for a second.

169
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,020
Got it.

170
00:10:14,130 --> 00:10:15,240
Do you know why

171
00:10:15,330 --> 00:10:16,990
you always score badly in math?

172
00:10:19,290 --> 00:10:20,280
I carefully analyzed

173
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,370
your papers and your solutions,

174
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:24,510
and found out that
you could remember some formulas

175
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,290
but couldn't use them correctly.

176
00:10:26,540 --> 00:10:27,420
Look at this.

177
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,720
You solved multiple-choice questions

178
00:10:28,810 --> 00:10:30,240
by merely applying formulas

179
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:31,710
without thinking at all.

180
00:10:33,070 --> 00:10:34,640
And you only filled in
these blanks randomly.

181
00:10:35,010 --> 00:10:36,420
Look at arithmetic questions backwards.

182
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:38,260
For the first question,

183
00:10:38,350 --> 00:10:39,920
you used the wrong formula
in the first step,

184
00:10:40,010 --> 00:10:41,310
so subsequent steps were all wrong.

185
00:10:41,890 --> 00:10:42,640
For the second question,

186
00:10:42,730 --> 00:10:44,050
although you used the right formula,

187
00:10:44,130 --> 00:10:45,630
you concluded a wrong answer.

188
00:10:46,350 --> 00:10:48,190
And you didn't answer
the last question at all.

189
00:10:49,350 --> 00:10:51,550
Do you realize what your problem is?

190
00:10:56,500 --> 00:10:57,240
Forget it.

191
00:10:57,330 --> 00:10:59,290
You can't understand
even though I tell you.

192
00:11:01,210 --> 00:11:02,760
Based on your condition,

193
00:11:02,850 --> 00:11:05,310
I'm going to make a plan
to train your solving skills,

194
00:11:06,150 --> 00:11:07,640
but I haven't figured out the best plan.

195
00:11:10,010 --> 00:11:11,590
Wow, so complicated.

196
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:13,120
Li Qing Tong.

197
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:14,600
since I promised to help you,

198
00:11:14,740 --> 00:11:16,030
I will do my best.

199
00:11:16,210 --> 00:11:18,790
But you cannot depend on me completely.

200
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:21,750
You should also find
your own way to learn.

201
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:25,610
I know you've been trying
to recite formulas,

202
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,500
but I have to remind you.

203
00:11:27,830 --> 00:11:30,480
If you don't make any progress
in the next exam,

204
00:11:30,650 --> 00:11:31,990
I'll surely quit.

205
00:11:33,820 --> 00:11:34,740
Don't worry.

206
00:11:35,210 --> 00:11:36,970
If I still score so badly
in the next test,

207
00:11:37,050 --> 00:11:38,260
I'll quit myself.

208
00:12:00,210 --> 00:12:01,640
To those who've answered all questions,

209
00:12:01,730 --> 00:12:03,870
check your solutions
as carefully as you can.

210
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:33,100
Let me tell you,

211
00:12:33,300 --> 00:12:35,230
I will surely succeed this time.

212
00:12:37,850 --> 00:12:38,730
Hey!

213
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:41,520
I'm 100 percent sure that I will!

214
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:43,720
I studied so hard
for the first time in my life.

215
00:12:43,810 --> 00:12:45,800
God will surely take care of me!

216
00:12:45,890 --> 00:12:46,770
Hey!

217
00:12:47,450 --> 00:12:48,600
Stop! You!

218
00:12:54,410 --> 00:12:59,170
[Monthly Math Exam]

219
00:13:01,950 --> 00:13:02,850
It's impossible.

220
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,420
I don't believe it.

221
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:06,340
It isn't true, is it?

222
00:13:26,130 --> 00:13:27,520
Compared to the grade last time,

223
00:13:27,610 --> 00:13:28,630
it's six points

224
00:13:28,770 --> 00:13:29,650
higher.

225
00:13:30,250 --> 00:13:32,430
A...a little progress has been made.

226
00:13:40,230 --> 00:13:41,650
What should I do?

227
00:13:42,110 --> 00:13:44,120
I'm feeling so nervous.

228
00:13:44,650 --> 00:13:47,030
Does it mean we are not a team anymore?

229
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,490
Li Qing Tong.

230
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,340
I'm tired.

231
00:13:51,970 --> 00:13:53,350
I give in to my fate!

232
00:13:53,990 --> 00:13:55,120
Forget it.

233
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,380
For the past several exams,

234
00:14:05,540 --> 00:14:07,110
I believe you've noticed the grades.

235
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:10,060
If I may conclude,

236
00:14:10,390 --> 00:14:11,900
many students' grades

237
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:14,010
have improved drastically.

238
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:15,460
What does that mean?

239
00:14:15,590 --> 00:14:17,180
That means the study group

240
00:14:17,260 --> 00:14:18,900
has played a positive role.

241
00:14:18,990 --> 00:14:19,870
Am I right?

242
00:14:23,530 --> 00:14:25,590
Wang Xiao Min, anything
you are not content with?

243
00:14:28,090 --> 00:14:29,020
Not at all.

244
00:14:29,610 --> 00:14:31,870
Stand up.
Tell us your thoughts

245
00:14:37,470 --> 00:14:38,740
What thoughts?

246
00:14:39,180 --> 00:14:40,290
About the study group!

247
00:14:40,370 --> 00:14:41,580
Tell us your opinion.

248
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:45,320
No opinion.

249
00:14:46,010 --> 00:14:47,350
It's just for fun.

250
00:14:49,890 --> 00:14:51,410
Fine. No opinion.

251
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:52,670
I'll ask someone else.

252
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:53,900
Fan Shui Shui.

253
00:14:58,930 --> 00:14:59,810
You deserve it.

254
00:15:01,490 --> 00:15:02,530
Sir,

255
00:15:02,930 --> 00:15:04,470
I have no opinion either.

256
00:15:05,180 --> 00:15:06,360
Neither has opinions, huh?

257
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:08,340
Fine.

258
00:15:08,930 --> 00:15:09,990
I have an opinion.

259
00:15:11,060 --> 00:15:13,210
Every one else has made improvements

260
00:15:13,570 --> 00:15:15,140
except for you two.

261
00:15:15,930 --> 00:15:16,810
Wang Xiao Min.

262
00:15:17,650 --> 00:15:18,640
You ranked about 80 in the midterm,

263
00:15:18,730 --> 00:15:20,390
but this time your ranking is 104.

264
00:15:20,510 --> 00:15:21,480
And you!

265
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:22,720
You ranked about 70 in the midterm,

266
00:15:22,810 --> 00:15:23,680
but 105 this time!

267
00:15:23,770 --> 00:15:25,070
Good for you!

268
00:15:25,690 --> 00:15:27,830
Ranking the same
by falling behind together!

269
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:30,380
Yes.

270
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:31,690
Yes?

271
00:15:31,810 --> 00:15:32,450
No.

272
00:15:32,530 --> 00:15:34,750
I mean, yes, you should criticize us, sir.

273
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:35,830
Our group

274
00:15:35,980 --> 00:15:38,080
is indeed full of holes.

275
00:15:38,290 --> 00:15:39,490
I think your group

276
00:15:39,570 --> 00:15:41,150
should split up.

277
00:15:42,830 --> 00:15:44,450
I agree with you, sir.
Do it!

278
00:15:44,540 --> 00:15:45,600
Yes, please, sir.

279
00:15:45,690 --> 00:15:46,710
Sit down.

280
00:15:48,690 --> 00:15:49,790
Wu Zhi Xun

281
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,860
You help Wang Xiao Min.

282
00:15:52,850 --> 00:15:54,010
Being with Li Qing Tong

283
00:15:54,090 --> 00:15:55,120
didn't help her improve at all.

284
00:15:55,210 --> 00:15:56,090
Instead, your ranking is affected.

285
00:15:56,170 --> 00:15:57,100
It's not appropriate.

286
00:15:57,190 --> 00:15:58,310
You help him.

287
00:15:58,920 --> 00:16:00,190
He's not stupid,

288
00:16:00,310 --> 00:16:02,180
just not disciplined enough.

289
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:03,890
You can control him if
you are in the same group.

290
00:16:05,930 --> 00:16:06,680
Sir.

291
00:16:06,770 --> 00:16:08,510
What about Li Qing Tong?

292
00:16:08,690 --> 00:16:09,870
You can team up with her.

293
00:16:11,570 --> 00:16:13,240
Haven't you been urging her
to study all the time?

294
00:16:13,370 --> 00:16:14,250
You have good grades

295
00:16:14,330 --> 00:16:15,810
and you are good friends.

296
00:16:15,900 --> 00:16:16,920
Perfect match!

297
00:16:17,010 --> 00:16:17,960
Fan Shui Shui.

298
00:16:18,050 --> 00:16:19,670
Replace her
to be with Duan Xiao.

299
00:16:20,230 --> 00:16:21,210
-No way.
-No way.

300
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,110
Sir.

301
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,780
There's no way to separate them.

302
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:27,790
Why not?

303
00:16:27,930 --> 00:16:28,720
I don't know.

304
00:16:28,810 --> 00:16:29,770
You should ask them.

305
00:16:29,850 --> 00:16:31,480
Lin Xue Wei, you prick!

306
00:16:31,570 --> 00:16:32,730
Sir, don't listen to her nonsense.

307
00:16:32,810 --> 00:16:33,640
You're the prick.

308
00:16:33,730 --> 00:16:34,540
Sir, he insulted me!

309
00:16:34,630 --> 00:16:35,510
You deserve...

310
00:16:38,660 --> 00:16:40,200
Enough!

311
00:16:42,050 --> 00:16:44,350
Why did I give you the right
to help each other?

312
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:47,590
Because I trusted you!

313
00:16:48,290 --> 00:16:49,370
You should take actions

314
00:16:49,460 --> 00:16:50,980
to reward my trust!

315
00:16:51,930 --> 00:16:53,940
What's the purpose of the study group?

316
00:16:55,010 --> 00:16:56,720
It's for supervising each other

317
00:16:56,800 --> 00:16:58,900
and learning from each other!

318
00:16:59,210 --> 00:17:01,390
I didn't ask you to have fun!

319
00:17:03,650 --> 00:17:04,480
If you dare to use this chance

320
00:17:04,569 --> 00:17:06,109
to do something else except for study,

321
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:07,569
I'll take the right back!

322
00:17:09,140 --> 00:17:10,020
Mr Wu.

323
00:17:10,869 --> 00:17:12,170
I also object to exchanging members.

324
00:17:13,650 --> 00:17:15,470
I want out.

325
00:17:16,810 --> 00:17:17,690
Why?

326
00:17:19,060 --> 00:17:19,829
I think

327
00:17:19,910 --> 00:17:21,510
I have no ability to tutor others.

328
00:17:21,869 --> 00:17:22,490
Besides,

329
00:17:22,579 --> 00:17:24,589
it has affected my own grades.

330
00:17:25,010 --> 00:17:26,740
So I want to quit.

331
00:17:30,940 --> 00:17:31,950
Mr Wu.

332
00:17:32,490 --> 00:17:33,780
Can't I quit?

333
00:17:35,300 --> 00:17:36,280
You can.

334
00:17:37,770 --> 00:17:38,990
Of course you can.

335
00:17:39,770 --> 00:17:40,760
Any student

336
00:17:40,850 --> 00:17:42,240
who thinks

337
00:17:42,330 --> 00:17:43,550
the study group

338
00:17:43,820 --> 00:17:45,050
has affected your own study

339
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:46,870
has the right to quit.

340
00:17:48,150 --> 00:17:49,210
But I think,

341
00:17:49,290 --> 00:17:51,550
this isn't something
that can be solved in class.

342
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,580
Meet me in my office. We'll talk alone.

343
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:55,090
Sit down, all of you.

344
00:17:58,650 --> 00:17:59,750
Get on with the class.

345
00:18:08,050 --> 00:18:08,950
Wu Zhi Xun.

346
00:18:10,330 --> 00:18:11,870
Are you really going to quit?

347
00:18:11,950 --> 00:18:12,820
Yes.

348
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:14,630
Then what about the promise?

349
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:16,760
She's recited everything
you've asked her to recite,

350
00:18:16,850 --> 00:18:17,670
but now you want to quit.

351
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:19,160
Aren't you giving up halfway?

352
00:18:19,250 --> 00:18:20,830
What's called "giving up halfway"?

353
00:18:20,980 --> 00:18:22,690
How long should I tutor her?

354
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:23,680
One year?

355
00:18:23,820 --> 00:18:24,750
Ten years?

356
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:26,000
Or my whole life?

357
00:18:37,900 --> 00:18:39,470
Go on, scold me.

358
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:41,860
I know you'll scold me again.

359
00:18:43,590 --> 00:18:44,640
No, I won't.

360
00:18:46,690 --> 00:18:48,710
I deserve it because I asked for it.

361
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:51,750
Nothing could be achieved after all.

362
00:19:00,660 --> 00:19:01,880
Wu Zhi Xun.

363
00:19:03,570 --> 00:19:04,730
Wu Zhi Xun!

364
00:19:06,250 --> 00:19:08,060
I know I didn't do well.

365
00:19:08,150 --> 00:19:09,590
I don't blame you.

366
00:19:09,810 --> 00:19:11,240
It's you who made the mistake,

367
00:19:11,330 --> 00:19:12,390
not me.

368
00:19:12,850 --> 00:19:14,050
I know.

369
00:19:14,130 --> 00:19:15,830
But I just want you to know

370
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:17,570
how hard I've studied.

371
00:19:17,650 --> 00:19:18,480
I've really tried my best.

372
00:19:18,570 --> 00:19:20,790
I didn't think studying was unimportant!

373
00:19:23,930 --> 00:19:24,800
Sorry.

374
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:26,460
Maybe I don't have the ability
to tutor you.

375
00:19:27,490 --> 00:19:28,590
In the future,

376
00:19:28,730 --> 00:19:30,300
we'll just be desk mates.

377
00:19:48,180 --> 00:19:48,760
Come on,

378
00:19:48,850 --> 00:19:50,110
let's go out to eat delicious food.

379
00:19:54,430 --> 00:19:56,270
So Wu Zhi Xun quit. It's not a big deal.

380
00:19:56,450 --> 00:19:58,350
Does it mean you can't study without him?

381
00:19:58,770 --> 00:20:00,000
He's always saying something harsh.

382
00:20:00,090 --> 00:20:01,340
You've really suffered a lot!

383
00:20:02,220 --> 00:20:03,100
You mean it?

384
00:20:04,490 --> 00:20:05,790
I thought

385
00:20:05,980 --> 00:20:07,500
you were also mad at me.

386
00:20:08,530 --> 00:20:09,870
No, I'm not mad.

387
00:20:10,610 --> 00:20:11,900
Let's go eat something delicious.

388
00:20:13,040 --> 00:20:14,740
I feel so relieved if you're not mad!

389
00:20:14,970 --> 00:20:15,770
Just eat these.

390
00:20:15,850 --> 00:20:16,560
Instant noodles are fine.

391
00:20:16,650 --> 00:20:17,670
No need to go out.

392
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,140
[And with that,]

393
00:20:20,330 --> 00:20:22,560
[the handsome mentor
I prepared for Li Qing Tong]

394
00:20:22,660 --> 00:20:25,250
[never tutored her again]

395
00:20:25,370 --> 00:20:26,750
[because of her 15-point score.]

396
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:28,650
[Maybe,]

397
00:20:28,730 --> 00:20:30,500
[this is her fate,]

398
00:20:30,650 --> 00:20:32,430
[which I couldn't change after all.]

399
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:40,310
[Essential Questions for
College Entrance Exam]

400
00:20:58,620 --> 00:21:00,680
[However, I didn't know]

401
00:21:01,290 --> 00:21:02,910
[what I thought was the end]

402
00:21:03,090 --> 00:21:04,760
[wasn't really the end]

403
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:04,890
[Li Qing Tong study plan]

404
00:21:04,890 --> 00:21:06,830
[for someone else.]

405
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:12,120
[And the end I thought was true]

406
00:21:12,640 --> 00:21:15,870
[made waves again
that were neither big nor small.]

407
00:21:20,580 --> 00:21:22,150
Big cities are great.

408
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:23,750
Quite true.

409
00:21:24,210 --> 00:21:25,550
Opportunities in Shenzhen

410
00:21:25,650 --> 00:21:26,870
are numerous!

411
00:21:27,130 --> 00:21:29,770
Find a chance to introduce Shenzhen
to Mr Wang.

412
00:21:29,900 --> 00:21:32,520
He's also considering going to Shenzhen.

413
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:34,040
Okay.

414
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:37,590
Who?

415
00:21:39,970 --> 00:21:41,070
You mean

416
00:21:41,170 --> 00:21:42,870
Ms Li from cooperatives?

417
00:21:45,260 --> 00:21:46,880
Did... Did you see her?

418
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:51,200
It's fine.

419
00:21:51,420 --> 00:21:53,190
Okay. Never mind.

420
00:21:53,900 --> 00:21:54,560
Okay.

421
00:21:54,650 --> 00:21:55,590
What?

422
00:21:56,370 --> 00:21:57,470
Was it Hua's mum?

423
00:22:00,020 --> 00:22:02,040
The saleswoman in our factory

424
00:22:02,210 --> 00:22:04,520
saw Hua's mum on the bus,

425
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,030
and greeted her.

426
00:22:09,030 --> 00:22:10,450
She's back from abroad?

427
00:22:19,180 --> 00:22:21,190
Hey, can you just stop tinkering with it?

428
00:22:22,610 --> 00:22:24,310
I'm talking to you!

429
00:22:24,950 --> 00:22:26,620
Li Wu Si! Did you hear me?

430
00:22:26,730 --> 00:22:27,950
I heard you.

431
00:22:28,100 --> 00:22:29,820
I've told you. Stop asking around!

432
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:30,710
You didn't listen to me!

433
00:22:30,810 --> 00:22:31,790
What do you want me to say?

434
00:22:31,940 --> 00:22:33,320
Why can't I ask?

435
00:22:33,610 --> 00:22:34,360
Isn't it obvious?

436
00:22:34,450 --> 00:22:36,200
It's not convenient to talk about it.

437
00:22:36,290 --> 00:22:37,560
I don't understand.

438
00:22:37,650 --> 00:22:39,120
Her mother has returned.

439
00:22:39,210 --> 00:22:40,000
But she neither picked her child up

440
00:22:40,090 --> 00:22:41,160
nor contacted us.

441
00:22:41,250 --> 00:22:43,310
It makes no sense
to ignore her child like this.

442
00:22:43,400 --> 00:22:44,990
What kind of a parent is she?

443
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:46,830
Stop talking nonsense!

444
00:22:46,960 --> 00:22:47,750
If the kid hears,

445
00:22:47,850 --> 00:22:50,070
she would think we're so mean
to throw her out!

446
00:22:51,550 --> 00:22:52,530
What did you say?

447
00:22:52,700 --> 00:22:53,870
Mean?

448
00:22:54,690 --> 00:22:56,760
Don't you know the condition
of our family?

449
00:22:56,890 --> 00:22:58,480
We cannot even feed ourselves!

450
00:22:58,570 --> 00:23:00,310
And you're still thinking about others!

451
00:23:01,090 --> 00:23:01,970
What?

452
00:23:02,120 --> 00:23:03,150
I'm just telling you the truth.

453
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:04,520
How dare you throw it!

454
00:23:04,610 --> 00:23:06,170
Mum, we're back!

455
00:23:07,330 --> 00:23:08,880
You girls are back!

456
00:23:08,970 --> 00:23:09,970
Wash your hands, now.

457
00:23:10,050 --> 00:23:11,790
I'll boil dumplings for you.

458
00:23:15,840 --> 00:23:17,780
What a double-face!

459
00:23:21,050 --> 00:23:23,610
Here comes the biggest dumplings
in the world!

460
00:23:23,690 --> 00:23:25,250
-Dumplings are ready.
-Here.

461
00:23:25,330 --> 00:23:26,000
Put it in the centre.

462
00:23:26,090 --> 00:23:27,230
Help yourselves!

463
00:23:31,300 --> 00:23:32,650
Turn on the TV.
I'll watch the news.

464
00:23:32,740 --> 00:23:33,800
Don't watch TV.

465
00:23:33,890 --> 00:23:35,510
We're having dinner!

466
00:23:36,060 --> 00:23:38,590
Mum, why are the dumplings
not as good as before?

467
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:41,020
Just be content.

468
00:23:41,100 --> 00:23:42,750
Make them yourself if you can.

469
00:23:48,150 --> 00:23:49,250
Hua, eat more.

470
00:23:49,330 --> 00:23:51,670
There won't be any delicious dumplings
if you go abroad.

471
00:23:54,530 --> 00:23:55,410
Hua.

472
00:23:56,170 --> 00:23:58,220
You see, you've been here for months.

473
00:23:58,370 --> 00:23:59,230
Have your parents

474
00:23:59,320 --> 00:24:00,510
contacted you?

475
00:24:02,170 --> 00:24:02,990
Yes, they have.

476
00:24:03,120 --> 00:24:04,320
They called.

477
00:24:04,450 --> 00:24:05,270
So,

478
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:08,080
are they just leaving you here to study?

479
00:24:08,290 --> 00:24:09,520
What are you talking about?

480
00:24:09,610 --> 00:24:10,480
How could they do that?

481
00:24:10,570 --> 00:24:12,420
I told you, they are abroad.

482
00:24:12,520 --> 00:24:13,390
Did they contact you?

483
00:24:13,490 --> 00:24:14,400
Did they call you?

484
00:24:14,490 --> 00:24:15,550
Did they tell you?

485
00:24:18,820 --> 00:24:20,940
Well, I have told my parents everything.

486
00:24:22,220 --> 00:24:23,600
See? She's told them.

487
00:24:24,010 --> 00:24:25,440
By the way, it's hard

488
00:24:25,550 --> 00:24:27,170
to contact us from abroad.

489
00:24:27,330 --> 00:24:28,920
You don't understand.
So ignorant!

490
00:24:29,010 --> 00:24:29,730
What?

491
00:24:29,810 --> 00:24:31,320
I know it's hard to contact from abroad

492
00:24:31,410 --> 00:24:34,000
but it's not hard to contact
us since they came back!

493
00:24:34,090 --> 00:24:34,960
They didn't come back.

494
00:24:35,050 --> 00:24:36,690
Yes. Your mum came back.

495
00:24:36,780 --> 00:24:37,960
Several days ago,
your mum was in Shenzhen.

496
00:24:38,050 --> 00:24:39,680
Our colleague saw her.

497
00:24:39,860 --> 00:24:41,370
You mum came back?

498
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:44,270
Who saw her?

499
00:24:44,380 --> 00:24:45,960
Our colleague!

500
00:24:46,250 --> 00:24:48,140
Forget it. Ignore what aunt said.

501
00:24:48,260 --> 00:24:49,520
It must be the wrong person.

502
00:24:50,130 --> 00:24:50,920
Flesh and blood as she is,

503
00:24:51,010 --> 00:24:52,550
how could she be the wrong person?

504
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:55,330
Maybe she came back to do
something urgent and then left.

505
00:24:55,420 --> 00:24:56,270
It's pretty normal.

506
00:24:56,370 --> 00:24:58,520
You see, she came back
in a hurry,

507
00:24:58,610 --> 00:24:59,890
and then she went back in a hurry.

508
00:24:59,970 --> 00:25:01,710
Yeah. That makes sense.

509
00:25:04,610 --> 00:25:05,550
Well,

510
00:25:06,290 --> 00:25:07,990
how about giving me your mother's
phone number?

511
00:25:08,330 --> 00:25:09,590
We'll have a chat.

512
00:25:10,070 --> 00:25:11,640
It's too expensive
to make international calls.

513
00:25:12,760 --> 00:25:13,640
Well,

514
00:25:13,910 --> 00:25:15,820
how about you give her our number.

515
00:25:15,910 --> 00:25:17,290
Let her phone me.

516
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:19,050
We must have a talk.

517
00:25:19,140 --> 00:25:19,840
Otherwise,

518
00:25:19,930 --> 00:25:21,590
I'm afraid your mother
is worried about you.

519
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:22,680
Okay?

520
00:25:23,790 --> 00:25:25,120
She's not worried at all.

521
00:25:26,210 --> 00:25:28,870
She may not be, but I am.

522
00:25:29,040 --> 00:25:30,800
You're all by yourself
in a foreign place.

523
00:25:30,890 --> 00:25:32,760
So if I don't talk to one of your parents

524
00:25:32,850 --> 00:25:34,770
about your condition now,

525
00:25:34,850 --> 00:25:36,560
do you think they can sleep well at night?

526
00:25:36,650 --> 00:25:38,630
They can't at all!

527
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,840
There's a time difference.

528
00:25:40,940 --> 00:25:42,370
It's not easy to make a phone call.

529
00:25:42,490 --> 00:25:43,920
Yes. Different time zone.

530
00:25:44,050 --> 00:25:45,130
Time zone.

531
00:25:45,220 --> 00:25:46,100
No.

532
00:25:46,210 --> 00:25:48,360
Hua, don't misunderstand me.

533
00:25:48,450 --> 00:25:49,320
I'm just wondering...

534
00:25:49,410 --> 00:25:50,830
Mum.

535
00:25:51,010 --> 00:25:52,640
Stop worrying about it!

536
00:25:52,730 --> 00:25:54,250
Of course her parents know her conditions.

537
00:25:54,330 --> 00:25:55,720
If not, she couldn't have transferred
to our school,

538
00:25:55,810 --> 00:25:57,330
or get any tuition fees, right?

539
00:25:57,410 --> 00:25:58,210
I agree.

540
00:25:58,290 --> 00:25:59,410
Stop worrying about it.

541
00:25:59,490 --> 00:26:02,140
Only your mum would do that. Really.

542
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:04,200
Even dumplings can't stop you
from talking, huh?

543
00:26:04,290 --> 00:26:05,950
Does it have anything to do with you?

544
00:26:06,410 --> 00:26:07,310
Li Qing Tong.

545
00:26:07,530 --> 00:26:09,920
Are you hoping
your dad and I are abroad?

546
00:26:10,010 --> 00:26:11,560
Then you could live happily
on the alien planet

547
00:26:11,650 --> 00:26:12,970
with nobody looking after you!

548
00:26:13,060 --> 00:26:14,440
You must be so happy, aren't you?

549
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:15,280
No way.

550
00:26:15,370 --> 00:26:17,070
You can go, but my dad can't.

551
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:18,790
I like what you said.

552
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:20,820
Stop eating.

553
00:26:21,530 --> 00:26:22,430
Get out. Stop eating.

554
00:26:22,530 --> 00:26:23,990
Stop, stop, stop...

555
00:26:24,450 --> 00:26:25,950
You're always threatening us like that!

556
00:26:26,050 --> 00:26:27,270
Heck!

557
00:26:27,990 --> 00:26:29,200
Help yourselves, girls.

558
00:26:29,290 --> 00:26:30,520
Hua, eat more.

559
00:26:30,610 --> 00:26:31,650
Hua, here you go.

560
00:26:31,730 --> 00:26:32,530
Eat more dumplings.

561
00:26:32,610 --> 00:26:33,490
Hua.

562
00:26:33,610 --> 00:26:34,410
Forget about your mum.

563
00:26:34,490 --> 00:26:35,830
If we don't communicate with her,

564
00:26:35,910 --> 00:26:36,910
how can I feel at ease?

565
00:26:38,330 --> 00:26:39,910
Stop worrying. Just eat.

566
00:26:40,010 --> 00:26:42,710
Is it hard for you
to keep quiet at dinner?

567
00:26:44,450 --> 00:26:46,030
Did your mum really come back?

568
00:26:48,890 --> 00:26:50,150
It's possible.

569
00:26:50,250 --> 00:26:51,660
She often goes back and forth.

570
00:26:52,600 --> 00:26:54,850
I think it's better to let your mother
talk to my mother,

571
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:57,820
or she won't stop nagging all day long.

572
00:27:01,730 --> 00:27:03,590
Let me tell you the truth.

573
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:05,210
Don't tell it to anyone.

574
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:06,780
What's happened?

575
00:27:13,910 --> 00:27:16,070
Tong, why did you ask us to gather?

576
00:27:18,590 --> 00:27:19,870
I'll say this in advance.

577
00:27:19,970 --> 00:27:22,200
No one is allowed
to tell it to their parents.

578
00:27:22,290 --> 00:27:23,490
Don't betray your friend.

579
00:27:23,570 --> 00:27:24,930
Definitely, we won't.

580
00:27:25,020 --> 00:27:26,100
What happened?

581
00:27:26,310 --> 00:27:29,060
Hua is studying here all by herself

582
00:27:29,210 --> 00:27:31,670
because there is a sad story behind it.

583
00:27:35,660 --> 00:27:36,520
My parents are divorced.

584
00:27:36,610 --> 00:27:38,040
I now live with my mum and stepfather.

585
00:27:38,130 --> 00:27:39,160
My mum went on a business trip

586
00:27:39,250 --> 00:27:40,400
and I didn't want to live
with my stepfather,

587
00:27:40,490 --> 00:27:42,070
so I sneaked out secretly.

588
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:46,200
I feel so happy to go to school with you,

589
00:27:46,330 --> 00:27:48,040
so I don't want to go back now.

590
00:27:48,130 --> 00:27:50,950
Please help me...

591
00:27:51,840 --> 00:27:54,120
We can't just sit here
watching Hua in such misery!

592
00:27:54,250 --> 00:27:55,680
We must help her!

593
00:27:55,770 --> 00:27:56,950
How can we help?

594
00:27:58,400 --> 00:27:59,130
Now,

595
00:27:59,210 --> 00:28:00,040
we should find an adult

596
00:28:00,130 --> 00:28:01,040
to pretend to be Hua's parent

597
00:28:01,130 --> 00:28:02,960
and call my parents.

598
00:28:03,050 --> 00:28:03,720
Once they talk,

599
00:28:03,810 --> 00:28:04,750
it will be settled.

600
00:28:09,650 --> 00:28:11,200
Would anyone like to help?

601
00:28:11,290 --> 00:28:11,920
Me!

602
00:28:12,010 --> 00:28:12,890
Yes?

603
00:28:13,010 --> 00:28:13,990
I can phone them myself.

604
00:28:14,550 --> 00:28:15,440
Piss off!

605
00:28:15,650 --> 00:28:16,870
What?

606
00:28:17,010 --> 00:28:18,730
I have a mature voice.

607
00:28:18,820 --> 00:28:20,030
Listen to this.

608
00:28:20,840 --> 00:28:21,810
Hello,

609
00:28:21,900 --> 00:28:22,920
is this Li Qing Tong's mother?

610
00:28:23,010 --> 00:28:24,280
Jesus Christ!

611
00:28:24,370 --> 00:28:26,530
Once you start talking,
my mum will recognize you right away!

612
00:28:26,610 --> 00:28:27,490
Really?

613
00:28:29,470 --> 00:28:30,350
Me!

614
00:28:31,530 --> 00:28:32,670
I'll let my dad do it.

615
00:28:33,530 --> 00:28:34,800
My dad kept personal money

616
00:28:34,890 --> 00:28:35,920
and I found out.

617
00:28:36,010 --> 00:28:36,890
He's been very nice to me.

618
00:28:36,980 --> 00:28:38,760
Your dad has known my dad for years.

619
00:28:38,850 --> 00:28:40,430
Do you think he can't recognize him?

620
00:28:41,070 --> 00:28:42,410
How about my uncle?

621
00:28:42,620 --> 00:28:43,850
He doesn't live here,

622
00:28:43,940 --> 00:28:45,070
so nobody has ever seen him.

623
00:28:46,450 --> 00:28:47,770
Deceiving adults to help kids

624
00:28:47,850 --> 00:28:49,470
won't be agreed by anyone.

625
00:28:51,260 --> 00:28:52,180
I have an idea.

626
00:28:52,270 --> 00:28:53,380
Leave it to me.

627
00:28:53,460 --> 00:28:54,490
Don't worry about it.

628
00:29:08,120 --> 00:29:09,000
Sis.

629
00:29:09,180 --> 00:29:10,570
Don't just eat the meat.

630
00:29:10,770 --> 00:29:11,800
Are you going to help me or not?

631
00:29:11,890 --> 00:29:12,790
No, I can't.

632
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:14,780
Why not?

633
00:29:16,060 --> 00:29:17,800
Why should I pretend to be a mother?

634
00:29:18,020 --> 00:29:19,450
Do I look as old as her mum?

635
00:29:19,530 --> 00:29:20,880
Of course you're not old.

636
00:29:21,010 --> 00:29:22,360
You're mature,

637
00:29:22,510 --> 00:29:23,390
stable

638
00:29:23,490 --> 00:29:24,650
and elegant.

639
00:29:24,740 --> 00:29:26,670
Then I can understand you.

640
00:29:27,320 --> 00:29:28,340
For what?

641
00:29:28,430 --> 00:29:29,520
To deceive someone?

642
00:29:29,610 --> 00:29:30,570
No.

643
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:32,290
I've told you.

644
00:29:32,580 --> 00:29:34,250
My classmate is so miserable.

645
00:29:34,480 --> 00:29:35,440
Just do us a favour.

646
00:29:35,540 --> 00:29:37,350
Make a phone cal
and say everything's alright.

647
00:29:37,650 --> 00:29:38,610
Nothing else.

648
00:29:38,690 --> 00:29:40,600
Are you sure there won't be anything else?

649
00:29:40,690 --> 00:29:42,070
You're all kids.

650
00:29:42,170 --> 00:29:43,360
What if an accident happens

651
00:29:43,450 --> 00:29:44,510
and her parents come to find me?

652
00:29:44,610 --> 00:29:45,920
I can't take the responsibility.

653
00:29:46,010 --> 00:29:47,260
No, you don't have to.

654
00:29:47,820 --> 00:29:49,890
I started taking baths
in your bathhouse since I was a kid.

655
00:29:49,990 --> 00:29:51,470
Don't you know what kind of person I am?

656
00:29:51,620 --> 00:29:53,690
Aren't you clear of my mum's personality?

657
00:29:53,810 --> 00:29:55,740
Am I that kind of bad kid?

658
00:29:57,690 --> 00:30:00,240
Kids also have their difficulties.

659
00:30:00,330 --> 00:30:01,200
I promise

660
00:30:01,290 --> 00:30:02,830
nothing will happen.

661
00:30:03,270 --> 00:30:04,700
I don't even trust them,

662
00:30:04,770 --> 00:30:06,000
only you.

663
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:07,600
You're just like my own sister.

664
00:30:07,720 --> 00:30:09,610
Please do me the favour, sis.

665
00:30:12,080 --> 00:30:13,670
A small present for you.

666
00:30:13,760 --> 00:30:14,940
It really suits you.

667
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:17,920
What is it?

668
00:30:18,020 --> 00:30:19,090
A sugar-coated bullet?

669
00:30:19,170 --> 00:30:20,480
It's not a sugar-coated bullet!

670
00:30:20,570 --> 00:30:22,350
Just to express my sincerity.

671
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:24,350
Please do me the favour.

672
00:30:24,530 --> 00:30:25,630
Sis.

673
00:30:27,450 --> 00:30:28,630
This is an exception, okay?

674
00:30:30,780 --> 00:30:31,950
What is it?

675
00:30:38,610 --> 00:30:40,670
Hua. Pick up the phone.

676
00:30:41,890 --> 00:30:42,770
Hello.

677
00:30:43,040 --> 00:30:44,430
Hello!

678
00:30:44,810 --> 00:30:47,200
Is this Li Qing Tong's house?

679
00:30:47,290 --> 00:30:48,950
Are you looking for Li Qing Tong?

680
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:52,330
I'm Li Jin Bu's mummy!

681
00:30:52,950 --> 00:30:53,830
Who?

682
00:30:54,700 --> 00:30:57,360
I...I'm Li Jin Bu's mother.

683
00:31:04,700 --> 00:31:06,480
Did Duan Xiao let you make the call?

684
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:07,660
Yes.

685
00:31:07,750 --> 00:31:08,630
Who are you?

686
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:13,350
Mum, why did you only call now?

687
00:31:14,250 --> 00:31:16,070
[I just finished my work.]

688
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,550
[How are you doing abroad?]

689
00:31:18,210 --> 00:31:19,730
I live at Li Qing Tong's home.

690
00:31:19,830 --> 00:31:20,440
It's very nice.

691
00:31:20,530 --> 00:31:22,120
The uncle and the auntie
are so nice to me.

692
00:31:22,210 --> 00:31:23,750
[The school is also nice.]

693
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,740
[Yes. Don't worry about me.]

694
00:31:26,850 --> 00:31:27,830
[Well...]

695
00:31:28,210 --> 00:31:30,550
I'll let Li Qing Tong's dad talk to you.

696
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:32,710
Okay, okay.

697
00:31:32,790 --> 00:31:33,770
Okay.

698
00:31:34,290 --> 00:31:36,510
Uncle, it's my mum.

699
00:31:36,930 --> 00:31:38,390
International phone call?

700
00:31:39,670 --> 00:31:40,550
Hello!

701
00:31:41,320 --> 00:31:42,430
Hello!

702
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,630
Hello!

703
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:45,380
You must be Brother Wu Si!

704
00:31:45,490 --> 00:31:48,080
I'm Li Jin Bu's mummy!

705
00:31:48,170 --> 00:31:49,800
How are you?

706
00:31:49,890 --> 00:31:51,870
Hello, Hua's mum.

707
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:54,340
We've been wanting to call you.

708
00:31:54,690 --> 00:31:57,000
I should have called you earlier.

709
00:31:57,130 --> 00:31:58,800
[Sorry to make you worry.]

710
00:31:58,890 --> 00:32:01,240
I sincerely apologize.

711
00:32:01,340 --> 00:32:02,590
[It's fine.]

712
00:32:02,740 --> 00:32:05,050
You're busy doing business abroad.

713
00:32:05,130 --> 00:32:06,270
You're busy people.

714
00:32:06,380 --> 00:32:07,250
I can understand.

715
00:32:07,330 --> 00:32:10,840
Hua said after transferring
to the local school,

716
00:32:10,930 --> 00:32:13,560
she's been living
in your house since then.

717
00:32:13,650 --> 00:32:15,360
She's troubled you.

718
00:32:15,450 --> 00:32:16,560
So sorry

719
00:32:16,650 --> 00:32:19,250
to make trouble for you!

720
00:32:19,330 --> 00:32:20,040
Hua's mother,

721
00:32:20,130 --> 00:32:22,010
please do not mention it.

722
00:32:22,090 --> 00:32:23,480
Your daughter

723
00:32:23,570 --> 00:32:24,560
is very thoughtful.

724
00:32:24,650 --> 00:32:25,410
From time to time,

725
00:32:25,490 --> 00:32:27,440
she helps my daughter with homework.

726
00:32:27,530 --> 00:32:29,280
Those two girls go to school together.

727
00:32:29,370 --> 00:32:31,310
It's good to have a companion.

728
00:32:31,770 --> 00:32:34,010
Thank you very much.

729
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:35,480
Brother Wu Si,

730
00:32:35,570 --> 00:32:36,770
when I finish my work,

731
00:32:36,860 --> 00:32:38,530
I'll pick her up soon!

732
00:32:38,620 --> 00:32:42,230
At that time, I'll thank you face to face!

733
00:32:42,610 --> 00:32:43,280
Brother.

734
00:32:43,370 --> 00:32:43,920
Okay.

735
00:32:44,010 --> 00:32:45,200
-Who's calling?
-Hello?

736
00:32:45,290 --> 00:32:46,160
Who's that? Who's calling?

737
00:32:46,250 --> 00:32:47,560
Hua's mum. An international call.

738
00:32:47,650 --> 00:32:48,320
Let me talk to her.

739
00:32:48,410 --> 00:32:49,480
Hello, brother?

740
00:32:49,570 --> 00:32:51,230
Hello...

741
00:32:53,210 --> 00:32:54,200
There's no sound.

742
00:32:54,290 --> 00:32:57,380
International calls have weak signals.
The call dropped.

743
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,580
What did she say?

744
00:33:01,330 --> 00:33:03,880
She mainly expressed her gratitude

745
00:33:03,970 --> 00:33:05,430
towards our family.

746
00:33:05,690 --> 00:33:07,600
She said that
if there was any chance,

747
00:33:07,690 --> 00:33:08,810
she would come to our house

748
00:33:08,900 --> 00:33:10,390
to express her gratitude.

749
00:33:11,110 --> 00:33:12,620
Let me tell you, Liu Feng Xia.

750
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:14,500
You have to admit it

751
00:33:14,940 --> 00:33:17,730
that people in big cities talk

752
00:33:17,820 --> 00:33:19,040
differently from us.

753
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:21,420
Chinese mixed with English,
it sounded great.

754
00:33:21,500 --> 00:33:22,420
Really?

755
00:33:22,500 --> 00:33:23,190
But I think

756
00:33:23,290 --> 00:33:24,640
it still sounds a little bit

757
00:33:24,730 --> 00:33:26,990
like Northeast Chinese accent.

758
00:33:27,450 --> 00:33:29,160
Our accent is so hard to change.

759
00:33:29,250 --> 00:33:30,550
Tell me more.

760
00:33:30,740 --> 00:33:32,090
What did she say?

761
00:33:33,520 --> 00:33:34,750
It's mainly what I've told you.

762
00:33:34,850 --> 00:33:36,170
International calls, you know,

763
00:33:36,250 --> 00:33:37,510
can't allow us to talk much.

764
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:40,120
You must be relieved
now that she called.

765
00:33:40,190 --> 00:33:42,150
Right? We're all relieved.

766
00:33:42,350 --> 00:33:43,230
Yes.

767
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:45,700
It's better now that
we've spoken to each other.

768
00:33:45,790 --> 00:33:46,980
Yeah...

769
00:33:47,190 --> 00:33:48,230
Trim the vegetables.

770
00:33:48,330 --> 00:33:49,370
I'm waiting to cook them!

771
00:33:49,450 --> 00:33:50,340
Okay.

772
00:33:52,410 --> 00:33:53,330
Hua,

773
00:33:53,420 --> 00:33:55,020
uncle really benefited from you!

774
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:57,710
This is my first time to pick up
an international call.

775
00:33:57,970 --> 00:33:59,270
Tell your mum later

776
00:33:59,350 --> 00:34:00,270
that you will live here

777
00:34:00,350 --> 00:34:02,060
without any concern.

778
00:34:02,440 --> 00:34:03,530
Thanks, uncle!

779
00:34:05,910 --> 00:34:06,940
Hello.

780
00:34:09,690 --> 00:34:10,679
Hello!

781
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,800
I'm Li Jin Bu's mummy.

782
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:13,639
What are you doing?

783
00:34:13,730 --> 00:34:15,310
Like a ghost!

784
00:34:15,810 --> 00:34:16,719
What are you doing?

785
00:34:16,810 --> 00:34:17,719
Feeling guilty?

786
00:34:17,810 --> 00:34:19,310
Why should I feel guilty?

787
00:34:19,610 --> 00:34:21,610
Deceiving others
doesn't make you feel guilty?

788
00:34:21,690 --> 00:34:22,420
Say it!

789
00:34:22,510 --> 00:34:23,810
When did you become Li Jin Bu's mum?

790
00:34:23,889 --> 00:34:25,520
It's rude to eavesdrop on others.

791
00:34:25,610 --> 00:34:27,150
How could you help the Swift Leg?

792
00:34:28,179 --> 00:34:29,449
The one who kicked your face?

793
00:34:30,540 --> 00:34:31,790
Don't mention it.

794
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:34,150
She picks on me at school all the time.

795
00:34:35,730 --> 00:34:37,360
Look at you.
Who's your family?

796
00:34:37,449 --> 00:34:38,830
You traitor!

797
00:34:39,330 --> 00:34:40,159
I didn't know it was her.

798
00:34:40,250 --> 00:34:41,530
She wasn't the one who asked for help.

799
00:34:41,610 --> 00:34:43,389
I just did him a favour.

800
00:34:44,790 --> 00:34:45,850
I see.

801
00:34:47,020 --> 00:34:48,480
Duan Xiao asked you for help, right?

802
00:34:48,570 --> 00:34:49,250
Give it back.

803
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:51,040
Gifts blind the eyes.

804
00:34:51,130 --> 00:34:52,560
What crap is this?

805
00:34:52,650 --> 00:34:53,940
You know nothing at all!

806
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:56,030
You know what?

807
00:34:56,159 --> 00:34:58,270
Tell me what Duan Xiao told you,

808
00:34:58,370 --> 00:35:00,150
or I'll dump all of your crap.

809
00:35:00,410 --> 00:35:02,190
Okay, I'll tell you!

810
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:07,130
To Hua in Shenzhen,

811
00:35:07,660 --> 00:35:09,360
I'm so sorry.

812
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:12,070
I lied because I have no choice.

813
00:35:12,170 --> 00:35:14,270
Please forgive me.

814
00:35:14,370 --> 00:35:16,560
I'm here to pray for you

815
00:35:16,650 --> 00:35:17,920
that you will be a success

816
00:35:18,010 --> 00:35:19,530
and a beauty

817
00:35:19,630 --> 00:35:21,840
and I'll transmit to you

818
00:35:21,930 --> 00:35:24,350
the universal power.

819
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:27,100
What are you doing here?

820
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:30,230
Did auntie say anything else?

821
00:35:30,410 --> 00:35:32,780
Why would she still nag
after the phone call?

822
00:35:33,030 --> 00:35:33,720
Nevertheless,

823
00:35:33,810 --> 00:35:36,120
Duan Xiao is more reliable than Egg.

824
00:35:36,210 --> 00:35:38,230
How can Egg compete with Duan Xiao?

825
00:35:39,010 --> 00:35:39,970
My mum told me

826
00:35:40,090 --> 00:35:41,170
there will be a gathering tomorrow.

827
00:35:41,250 --> 00:35:42,350
She asked us to go together.

828
00:35:42,450 --> 00:35:43,320
A gathering?

829
00:35:43,410 --> 00:35:44,630
What gathering?

830
00:35:49,130 --> 00:35:50,670
It's so terrible!

831
00:35:50,870 --> 00:35:53,930
I thought they would buy us
beautiful clothes!

832
00:35:54,490 --> 00:35:56,600
They just bought grains and oil! What for?

833
00:35:56,690 --> 00:35:57,980
I wouldn't have come here if I knew!

834
00:35:58,570 --> 00:36:00,500
I think it's pretty fun.

835
00:36:00,650 --> 00:36:01,830
So lively.

836
00:36:03,090 --> 00:36:04,350
Do you want to eat frozen pears?

837
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:05,720
-Get some.
-Eat some.

838
00:36:05,810 --> 00:36:07,110
No, thanks.

839
00:36:08,210 --> 00:36:09,190
I've eaten enough.

840
00:36:09,740 --> 00:36:10,940
It's delicious.

841
00:36:11,050 --> 00:36:12,110
Egg Wang!

842
00:36:12,770 --> 00:36:14,520
Auntie, uncle, why are you here?

843
00:36:15,220 --> 00:36:16,560
What are you doing here alone?

844
00:36:16,650 --> 00:36:18,090
I came here to draw a lottery.

845
00:36:18,250 --> 00:36:19,160
Where is it?

846
00:36:19,340 --> 00:36:20,420
Didn't you hear it from the speaker?

847
00:36:20,510 --> 00:36:22,150
First prize is a cell phone.

848
00:36:22,420 --> 00:36:23,120
You believe it?

849
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:24,870
It must be a trick.

850
00:36:25,300 --> 00:36:26,790
What a silly child!

851
00:36:27,730 --> 00:36:28,950
So silly.

852
00:36:29,260 --> 00:36:30,130
Congratulations!

853
00:36:30,210 --> 00:36:31,760
The winner of the first prize!

854
00:36:31,850 --> 00:36:33,350
Bravo!

855
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:35,160
[First Prize]

856
00:36:35,770 --> 00:36:36,590
What?

857
00:36:36,680 --> 00:36:37,470
Dad!

858
00:36:37,610 --> 00:36:38,930
Didn't you say it was a trick?

859
00:36:39,010 --> 00:36:40,960
Why did he get the prize?

860
00:36:44,140 --> 00:36:45,930
Dear, give me 50 yuan.

861
00:36:46,020 --> 00:36:47,120
I'll also draw the lottery.

862
00:36:47,210 --> 00:36:49,860
[Prize]

863
00:36:53,130 --> 00:36:55,060
Thirty bars of soaps.

864
00:36:55,570 --> 00:36:57,600
You won 30 bars of soaps!

865
00:36:57,750 --> 00:36:59,520
It'd be better if you had won
a tube of toothpaste!

866
00:37:02,120 --> 00:37:03,860
Wash your hands twice.

867
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,590
We have plenty of soap anyway.

868
00:37:08,180 --> 00:37:09,080
As far as I'm concerned.

869
00:37:09,170 --> 00:37:10,320
Li Wu Si,

870
00:37:10,410 --> 00:37:12,800
stop thinking you'd get lucky
if you aren't destined to.

871
00:37:12,890 --> 00:37:14,870
Want to invest in stocks?

872
00:37:15,290 --> 00:37:16,710
What a daydreamer!

873
00:37:17,690 --> 00:37:19,430
It's totally different.

874
00:37:19,610 --> 00:37:21,710
Stock market is now a bull market.

875
00:37:21,810 --> 00:37:23,740
Others have earned from it.

876
00:37:24,430 --> 00:37:25,510
Besides,

877
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:27,950
I always have pretty good luck.

878
00:37:28,050 --> 00:37:29,940
The truth has proven it.

879
00:37:30,030 --> 00:37:31,890
What truth?

880
00:37:32,450 --> 00:37:33,750
All my life,

881
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:35,670
I've gathered all my luck

882
00:37:35,770 --> 00:37:37,910
and used it all up

883
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:40,380
to marry you, am I right?

884
00:37:44,650 --> 00:37:46,230
Kids are here.

885
00:37:46,620 --> 00:37:48,110
Don't be angry anymore.

886
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:51,180
Go wash hands.

887
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:54,760
Kids are here. Don't talk like that.

888
00:37:55,510 --> 00:37:56,450
Don't be angry anymore.

889
00:37:56,540 --> 00:37:58,050
Pick up those soaps.

890
00:38:03,790 --> 00:38:05,290
Here you are.

891
00:38:07,030 --> 00:38:08,430
Thank you, Mrs Peony.

892
00:38:09,420 --> 00:38:10,550
I didn't add too much chilli to it.

893
00:38:10,650 --> 00:38:11,720
Xiao said you can't eat spicy food.

894
00:38:11,810 --> 00:38:13,360
I can eat a little bit now.

895
00:38:13,450 --> 00:38:14,160
Really?

896
00:38:14,250 --> 00:38:15,510
Have a try.

897
00:38:20,830 --> 00:38:21,540
Delicious.

898
00:38:21,730 --> 00:38:23,550
Eat more if you like it.

899
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:27,720
Personally,

900
00:38:27,810 --> 00:38:29,510
I've always wanted a daughter.

901
00:38:29,970 --> 00:38:31,200
Such an impossible wish

902
00:38:31,290 --> 00:38:32,810
was accidentally achieved.

903
00:38:32,890 --> 00:38:34,600
God suddenly brought me a daughter.

904
00:38:34,690 --> 00:38:36,200
How lucky I am!

905
00:38:38,040 --> 00:38:39,460
From now on,

906
00:38:40,490 --> 00:38:42,140
you and Xiao are siblings.

907
00:38:44,520 --> 00:38:45,580
What are you talking about?

908
00:38:45,690 --> 00:38:47,010
Why are we siblings?

909
00:38:47,090 --> 00:38:48,230
What's wrong with being siblings?

910
00:38:48,330 --> 00:38:50,120
Are siblings closer or good friends?

911
00:38:50,230 --> 00:38:51,460
Siblings are not close at all.

912
00:38:51,550 --> 00:38:53,410
Only good friends
have opportunities to kis...

913
00:38:55,200 --> 00:38:57,100
To have fun together.

914
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,750
I'll get you the meal.

915
00:39:03,030 --> 00:39:05,370
I really like Mrs Peony.

916
00:39:06,200 --> 00:39:07,650
Then regard her as your mum.

917
00:39:09,970 --> 00:39:12,910
Since I came here,
I have got several mums.

918
00:39:13,010 --> 00:39:13,920
I'm not short of mums, to be honest.

919
00:39:14,010 --> 00:39:15,350
I'm short of dads.

920
00:39:17,210 --> 00:39:19,150
And your dad? Where is he?

921
00:39:19,250 --> 00:39:20,570
My dad is stationed
at the frontier.

922
00:39:20,650 --> 00:39:22,070
He only comes home
once in a few years.

923
00:39:22,160 --> 00:39:24,020
I mentioned you to him last night
when he called.

924
00:39:24,810 --> 00:39:25,850
Mentioned me?

925
00:39:25,930 --> 00:39:28,000
I said you were a new friend I made.

926
00:39:28,090 --> 00:39:29,710
My dad said you had a beautiful name.

927
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:32,650
Your dad has good taste.

928
00:39:32,890 --> 00:39:34,670
I'll bring you to where
my dad is stationed.

929
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:36,100
He's in Mohe County,
the northern-most of China.

930
00:39:36,210 --> 00:39:37,210
It's so beautiful!

931
00:39:37,300 --> 00:39:38,250
Sounds good.

932
00:39:40,980 --> 00:39:41,930
Did you

933
00:39:42,030 --> 00:39:44,630
have a bad time back in your own family?

934
00:39:46,520 --> 00:39:47,900
Just so-so.

935
00:39:48,900 --> 00:39:51,170
So, did your stepfather and others

936
00:39:51,250 --> 00:39:52,790
bully you?

937
00:39:54,990 --> 00:39:56,880
No, not that miserable.

938
00:39:57,030 --> 00:39:58,650
I'm used to it.

939
00:39:59,090 --> 00:40:00,350
Then don't go back.

940
00:40:00,640 --> 00:40:01,640
Why go back?

941
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:02,890
Stay here.

942
00:40:03,240 --> 00:40:04,560
When you go to college,

943
00:40:04,720 --> 00:40:05,730
I'll accompany you.

944
00:40:06,150 --> 00:40:07,340
If they dare to bully you,

945
00:40:07,450 --> 00:40:08,830
I'll fight against them!

946
00:40:09,700 --> 00:40:10,910
Are you going home with me?

947
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:12,560
Yes. I should protect you.

948
00:40:13,690 --> 00:40:14,800
Do you know where I live?

949
00:40:14,890 --> 00:40:15,880
Don't be silly!

950
00:40:15,970 --> 00:40:16,690
I'll go with you anywhere.

951
00:40:16,770 --> 00:40:18,060
Even the North or South Poles.

952
00:40:18,150 --> 00:40:19,250
Nothing to be afraid of.

953
00:40:20,900 --> 00:40:21,100
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

954
00:40:21,100 --> 00:40:22,520
Bo Ya was good at playing guqin.

955
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:24,660
Zhong Zi Qi was good
at appreciating music.

956
00:40:24,970 --> 00:40:26,320
When Bo Ya was playing the guqin,

957
00:40:26,430 --> 00:40:27,610
he was thinking about the mountains.

958
00:40:27,700 --> 00:40:28,860
Zhong Zi Qi said,

959
00:40:28,940 --> 00:40:30,040
"How beautiful!

960
00:40:30,130 --> 00:40:31,850
It's as high as Mount Tai!"

961
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:33,520
When he was thinking about
the flowing water,

962
00:40:33,770 --> 00:40:35,040
Zhong Zi Qi said,

963
00:40:35,130 --> 00:40:36,210
"How beautiful!

964
00:40:36,290 --> 00:40:38,480
It's as grand as Changjiang River!"

965
00:40:38,560 --> 00:40:39,630
Every time Bo Ya thought something,

966
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:41,270
Zhong Zi Qi could tell
what he was thinking.

967
00:40:41,350 --> 00:40:42,550
When Zi Qi died,

968
00:40:42,670 --> 00:40:45,050
Bo Ya said, "No one can
understand me anymore!"

969
00:40:45,140 --> 00:40:47,100
He smashed the guqin to pieces

970
00:40:47,190 --> 00:40:48,960
and never played it again.

971
00:40:49,410 --> 00:40:50,490
What does it mean?

972
00:40:52,130 --> 00:40:53,580
His closest confidante

973
00:40:53,910 --> 00:40:54,930
died.

974
00:40:55,370 --> 00:40:56,390
With the friend gone,

975
00:40:56,890 --> 00:40:58,470
he never played it again.

976
00:40:58,810 --> 00:40:59,760
What kind of friend is that?

977
00:40:59,870 --> 00:41:01,330
A true friend!

978
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:02,820
Wang Xiao Min

979
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:05,180
Stand up. Tell us what a friend is.

980
00:41:13,030 --> 00:41:14,470
Friends...

981
00:41:18,540 --> 00:41:21,190
walk together.

982
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:25,520
♫ No better days in the future ♫

983
00:41:25,610 --> 00:41:26,410
Sing with me.

984
00:41:26,510 --> 00:41:27,990
-♫ One word... ♫
-Sit down.

985
00:41:28,600 --> 00:41:29,870
I don't need you to tell me.

986
00:41:30,380 --> 00:41:31,880
I've heard it from Emil Chau.

987
00:41:34,890 --> 00:41:35,870
Tell me,

988
00:41:36,030 --> 00:41:38,010
the study group is no more.

989
00:41:38,200 --> 00:41:39,680
Why didn't Mr Wu change our seats back?

990
00:41:39,780 --> 00:41:40,870
You want to change it back?

991
00:41:41,020 --> 00:41:41,930
Of course not.

992
00:41:42,030 --> 00:41:43,560
I still want Wu Zhi Xun to tutor me.

993
00:41:43,650 --> 00:41:45,110
Is he still tutoring you?

994
00:41:45,310 --> 00:41:46,420
I'm trying.

995
00:41:46,570 --> 00:41:48,430
I need to rebuild my good image.

996
00:42:13,010 --> 00:42:14,310
What a coincidence.

997
00:42:28,260 --> 00:42:29,860
I know you come here every evening,

998
00:42:29,950 --> 00:42:32,170
so I just waited for you here.

999
00:42:32,550 --> 00:42:34,340
How do you know where I am?

1000
00:42:36,890 --> 00:42:38,090
That day, well...

1001
00:42:38,170 --> 00:42:39,950
I...I happened to see you.

1002
00:42:42,920 --> 00:42:45,020
Listen, I'm fully prepared this time.

1003
00:42:45,100 --> 00:42:46,070
About formulas and solutions

1004
00:42:46,170 --> 00:42:48,040
we've learned in the last term,

1005
00:42:48,130 --> 00:42:49,240
I have figured them all out.

1006
00:42:49,330 --> 00:42:50,760
Really, I mean it.

1007
00:42:50,850 --> 00:42:52,360
If you pick up any one of these exercises,

1008
00:42:52,450 --> 00:42:53,680
I can solve it.

1009
00:42:53,770 --> 00:42:56,470
We're not in the same group anymore.

1010
00:42:58,550 --> 00:42:59,520
I know.

1011
00:42:59,620 --> 00:43:00,360
But...

1012
00:43:00,450 --> 00:43:02,410
But we used to be partners.

1013
00:43:02,490 --> 00:43:04,120
That wasn't so bad, right?

1014
00:43:04,210 --> 00:43:05,150
So

1015
00:43:05,270 --> 00:43:06,640
don't give up halfway.

1016
00:43:11,560 --> 00:43:13,070
Did I interrupt you?

1017
00:43:13,160 --> 00:43:14,260
Yes, you did.

1018
00:43:31,020 --> 00:43:31,840
Since I'm here already,

1019
00:43:31,930 --> 00:43:33,600
I must review for a while.

1020
00:43:33,690 --> 00:43:35,150
Just partner up this time.

1021
00:43:36,020 --> 00:43:37,730
Please be quiet.

1022
00:43:37,850 --> 00:43:39,230
Thank you.

1023
00:43:40,690 --> 00:43:41,860
You're welcome.

1024
00:44:03,800 --> 00:44:05,140
Li Qing Tong!

1025
00:44:06,010 --> 00:44:07,580
It's really you!

1026
00:44:08,010 --> 00:44:09,710
I dared not call you just now at the door.

1027
00:44:10,340 --> 00:44:11,680
Be quiet!

1028
00:44:12,270 --> 00:44:13,640
What are you doing here?

1029
00:44:13,730 --> 00:44:15,070
Reading a novel?

1030
00:44:18,160 --> 00:44:19,460
You're studying?

1031
00:44:19,690 --> 00:44:21,030
Stop making noise, okay?

1032
00:44:21,210 --> 00:44:24,040
This is the library.
Do you have any morals?

1033
00:44:24,740 --> 00:44:27,040
What? I didn't talk aloud anyway.

1034
00:44:35,670 --> 00:44:37,150
I know why you are here.

1035
00:44:37,230 --> 00:44:38,770
Why mess with him again?

1036
00:44:39,430 --> 00:44:40,560
Study groups have come to an end,

1037
00:44:40,660 --> 00:44:42,030
but you two haven't, have you?

1038
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:43,390
Stop talking nonsense!

1039
00:44:43,490 --> 00:44:45,000
Get out of here!

1040
00:44:45,090 --> 00:44:47,150
What? What's wrong with you?

1041
00:44:48,850 --> 00:44:49,870
Get out.

1042
00:44:50,760 --> 00:44:51,710
Fine, fine.

1043
00:44:51,800 --> 00:44:53,260
How fierce you are!

1044
00:44:54,650 --> 00:44:55,800
Li Qing Tong.

1045
00:44:56,330 --> 00:44:57,330
You can do it!

1046
00:44:58,780 --> 00:45:00,040
You can do it!

1047
00:45:08,590 --> 00:45:09,610
Li Qing Tong.

1048
00:45:12,770 --> 00:45:15,070
You've read that page for 20 minutes.

1049
00:45:19,350 --> 00:45:21,270
Oh. It was all Fan Shui Shui's fault.

1050
00:45:21,450 --> 00:45:22,630
She interrupted me.

1051
00:45:24,930 --> 00:45:26,700
She affected my thought process.

1052
00:45:29,690 --> 00:45:31,190
Why did you turn so many pages?

1053
00:45:31,460 --> 00:45:33,070
Don't you need to read those pages?

1054
00:45:37,570 --> 00:45:39,590
You were reading Page 45 and 46.

1055
00:45:39,720 --> 00:45:41,670
Now you should read Page 47.

1056
00:45:42,090 --> 00:45:43,710
Why did you turn more than 20 pages?

1057
00:46:03,260 --> 00:46:04,730
Are you leaving now?

1058
00:46:06,030 --> 00:46:07,700
Will you come here tomorrow?

1059
00:46:08,010 --> 00:46:09,350
I'll come here tomorrow.

1060
00:46:10,640 --> 00:46:12,300
If you want me to keep tutoring you,

1061
00:46:12,680 --> 00:46:14,190
there is a prerequisite.

1062
00:46:14,550 --> 00:46:15,650
What is it?
